<note id="fs-idm341865440" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm512768080"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 9.6 Challenges of the 21st Century</para>
<para id="fs-idm470572304"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm336542416"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 9F Explain the causes and effects of the domestic and international challenges the United States has faced in the 21st century</para>
<para id="fs-idm517095632"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 9.3.II.B</para>
<para id="fs-idm506274928"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-1 Developments and Processes, HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
